short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a Subscribr Video Breakdown button to YouTube video pages.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Analyze a YouTube video's tone, structure, hooks, CTAs, and much more with Subscribr's Video Breakdown tool.

This extension adds a Subscribr logo icon to all YouTube video pages. Just click the icon on any YouTube video to view the breakdown on Subscribr.ai.
